The `lower/coerce.rs` handles general `Coerce` instructions (boxing/unboxing). My changes only touch `lower/expr.rs` and `lower/match_.rs` for the `Is` instruction lowering. There's no overlap with `coerce.rs`. The RT.2b lane (which touches coerce/Index lowering) operates on different sites.

